map_editor

Class Map

  • java.lang.Object
    • map_editor.Map

  • public class Map
extends java.lang.Object
    The function of Map class is to fill screen background with smaller images and set positions of game objects.To use this class user must fill its matrix(map,spriteList and backgraundImages.The value before # at matrix[y][x] is the index of image in backgraundImages which will be draw at position(x*filedWidth,y*filedHeight).The value after is the index of Sprite2D in spriteList which move to position(x*filedWidth,y*filedHeight).
    Author:
    Comexetina
